en.name: Singuard Arms Wages of Sin Skeletonized AR-15
en.description: Skeletonised AR-15 manufactured by Singuard Arms.

en.name: Singuard Arms AR-15 Buffer Tube
en.description: Finely tuned buffer extension for the Singuard Arms Wages of Sin AR-15 platform.

en.name: Singuard Arms Wages of Sin Handguard
en.description: Carbon fiber handguard for the Singuard Arms Wages of Sin AR-15 platform. Open and lightweight construction offers optimal ergonomics and nominal cooling factor to the barrel.

en.name: Singuard Arms Wages of Sin Upper Receiver
en.description: Skeletonised upper receiver for the Singuard Arms Wages of Sin AR-15 platform. The precision machining cuts on the billet upper offer reduced felt weight and increased ergonomics for the end user.

en.name: Singuard Arms Wages of Sin 5.56x45mm Muzzle Brake
en.description: A specially tuned muzzle brake for the Singuard Arms Wages of Sin AR-15 platform that greatly reduces felt recoil.

en.name: Singuard Arms Wages of Sin Pistol Grip
en.description: A skeletonised and ergonomic pistol grip for the Singuard Arms Wages of Sin AR-15 platform.

en.name: Singuard Arms Wages of Sin Stock
en.description: A carbon fiber wireframe stock for the Singuard Arms Wages of Sin AR-15 platform designed specifically to fit on Singuard Arms AR-15 buffer tubes.

en.name: Singuard Arms Wages of Sin AR-15 Charging Handle
en.description: A skeletonised charging handle for the Singuard Arms Wages of Sin AR-15 platform.
